}


### verify and activate user account
# return status 200 -> sucessfully verified
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify/{{validationToken}}


### login user
# return status 200 -> successfully logged in
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
content-type: application/json

{
 "username": "bllabla-1",
 "passwd": "Allt.xp-c0hrhhn@yopmail.com"
}

### get current user profile
# return status 200 -> successfully fetched user profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}